          "settings": {
            "heading": "<strong>The Marinière</strong>",
            "heading_size": "h2"
          }
        },
        "template--19520181272924__5b3ea410-b7bd-4f4b-905e-9ece045d2215-text-1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>When it comes to iconic apparel, few items combine timeless style and function like the Marinière. Much like blue jeans, this traditional striped shirt has evolved over the past century, transforming from a practical uniform worn by sailors into an everyday staple for men and women around the world. The Marinière certainly isn’t tied to a particular time of year either - one of the best things about it is its year-round appeal.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
