        "a5c2d658-cc61-49e3-8540-d59ba92f7197": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>This is our first drop. Only 99 marinières produced.</p><p>Made in a breathable mid-weight knit cotton yarn that makes it perfect for any season.<br/>The fit is oversized, but don't worry, it will make you look great! </p><p>As there are so few pieces, we suggest you pre-order your marinière to avoid missing out. <a href=\"https://ateliermariniere.com/pages/pre-order\">Find out more</a>.</p>"
